How to create pv using hostpath
================================
when you need local volume of work node. then we have two way.

1) hostpath : hostPath that mounts the node's disk inside the containe. if your pod is pinned up on another node where the hostPath is not there, there can be inconsistencies, but there are certain use cases for the usage of hostPath.
2) local path :
3) emptyDir (partial peding)

IQ) difference between local and hostpath?
   => In hostpath api create folder automatically where local not. in local volume you will get volume only where you want like on node1.
      then when your container run on node2. it will not get folder there.

hostpath volume
 => when you application required local volume in readonly mode from work-node.(from node where container running.)


